metadata.name: Balloon Poppers #1
metadata.description: Balloon Poppers is a Gamified NFT collection of 4K Pixel Balloons that will begin to pop 60 mins after mint. Once started, balloons will pop once every 2 hours, until only 9 Balloons remain (1 of each color). There is no rhyme or reason to each popped balloon and winners will be chosen by blind luck.
